I put one star because zero wasn't an option. Do not order from this place. I ordered two pizzas, buffalo chicken wings, and a two liter of coke. When they charged me I questioned the $49.00 charge. They admitted that they made a mistake and reswipped the card for $34.00 the second time.  So when I pulled up my account that night I noticed they double charged me for my order for both amounts. So I called them and they told me that they would credit my card the one charge for $49.00.  A week later I checked my account and the credit still wasn't there. So I drove there to question why the credit wasn't issued back to my card. They told me to wait a week longer because it could take five to ten business days to go through.  So a week later there still was no credit. So I drove back to the place a second time and questioned why it wasn't credited. They then denied everything and refused to give me my credit which they promised to do. I'm sorry but two pizzas, buffalo chicken wings, and a two liter of coke should not cost $83.00 no where.  So I then called my credit card company and disputed the charges. I did not sign a receipt for the larger charge. The bank did credit my account for the amount.
